BUS1_01 'Bus Driver'
BUSTUT Press the ~h~~k~~TOGGLE_SUBMISSIONS~ button~w~ to toggle bus missions on or off. Bus missions are only available between 6 AM and 10 PM.
BUSTUT2 Press the ~h~~k~~TOGGLE_SUBMISSIONS~ button~w~ to toggle bus missions on or off. Bus missions are only available between 6 AM and 10 PM.
BUSNEXT Drive to the next stop.
BUSSTOP Stop in the blue area to load or unload passengers, if there are any.
BUSCANC Bus mission cancelled.
BUSCANN Bus mission cancelled. It is night time! You need to rest until 6 AM to start a bus mission.
BUSFULL The bus is full! Drive to the next stop.
BUSBON Route completed! Bonus: $~1~
BUSLATE It is night time! No bus missions available.